          "en": "A description of any methods implemented in data acquisition or processing, if any, to detect the presence of unsuitable data sources considering the model's intended uses, including but not limited to illegal content, child sexual abuse material (CSAM), non-consensual intimate imagery (NCII), and personal data leading to its unlawful processing."
