      "inpackage": "UNKNOWN",
      "label-en": {
        "en": "has quality measurement"
      },
      "definition-en": {
        "en": "Metrics that can be performed to assess the quality of any kind of resource (e.g., a dataset, a linkset, a graph, a set of triples). However, in the DQV context, it is generally expected to be used in statements in which subjects are instances of dcat:Dataset or dcat:Distribution."
      },
